Body: Lead time as of December is ~4-5 weeks (some colors in stock; ship in 1-2 weeks), a fraction of other manufacturers!See StellarSpas.com for Must Have Options Package discount (Recommended Options list).American made and built with the highest quality Lucite acrylic shells, Gecko digital controls, 4.5 kW heater, and Del ozonators, these spas directly compare to those selling in showrooms for $2K+ more. Stellar Spas has been selling this line of spas for a decade. In that time, we've had only a small handful warranty issues involving a major component. We've been in business 23 years and have an A+ Rating with the BBB.The St. Tropez (1st photo) is a very popular 5-person, 88 stainless jets, 10 hp (one 6-hp pump and one 4-hp 2-speed pump) hot tub. Curbside delivery is included in the price. Note: All prices subject to change at any time.  See website for current discount.Beware of underpowered spas! It's all about true hydrotherapy, which means 220V & TWO BIG pumps. Enjoy a deep tissue hydrotherapy massage, then turn down the 2-speed pump and relax if you choose. Compare to other 110V spas with small heaters (struggling to maintain proper temp) and small or a single pump, which really only recirculate the water.Also beware of others whose base price doesn't include ozone filtration (helps kill bacteria), covers or delivery. These are things you *must have* and will add hundreds to your price. Thermal covers and ozonators are all standard with ours.  Curbside delivery is also included to most states.Other popular models shown as well. Add $175 to St. Tropez and Monaco models for Motion Glow lighting (individual LED lights along upper inside edge of shell). See "LED LIGHTING VIDEO" lighting on our website. Motion Glow LED Lighting comes standard on St. Lucia and Beaumont models.NO SALES TAX for AL deliveries!CURBSIDE DELIVERY INCLUDE IN PRICEGecko controls are a state-of-the-art component in the spa industry; at the height of programming technology and high quality craftsmanship. Title: Dehumidifier. Fantastic!!!
Body: Lightly used:Fantastic!Rugged and high-performing, the Ebac PD200 Dehumidifier (1028250) tames humidity and stops mold and mildew damage in damp interior spaces. This heavy duty dehumidifier reduces excess humidity, kills moisture-craving bacteria, and removes damaging condensation from windows, walls, and ceilings.It's a self-contained all-steel appliance that is capable of removing 190 pints of water vapor per day. Plus, like its smaller sibling, the Ebac PD120, the PD200 features a quiet two-speed fan, an adjustable humidistat, and an automatic defrost mode for continuous and reliable operation.The Ebac PD200 Commercial Dehumidifier is primarily designed for use in harsh marine environments. However, because of its installation and feature flexibility, the unit also works effectively in:Health and Fitness CentersSports HallsAerobic RoomsRacquetball/Handball CourtsWorkout AreasLocker RoomsLaundry RoomsWarehousesStadiumsSimple Controls, Automatic DefrostThe Ebac PD200 Dehumidifier has a number of simple control features that help make no-hassle and energy-efficient operation possible. The unit's adjustable humidistat helps you save energy and money by cycling the fan on and off intermittently while it maintains your desired humidity setting.In addition, this spa and pool dehumidifier features a temperature-sensitive "Reverse Cycle" defrost setting. This electronic function automatically melts away frost buildup on the unit's internal coils in order to continue effective operation in low ambient temperatures.Easy Installation and SetupThis Ebac dehumidifier offers you the benefit of headache-free installation. Title: Covermore 40x40x15 (30oz PVC) Double TRUSS Shipping Container Shelter
Body: COVERMORE**PLEASE NOTE: AVAILABLE FOR DELIVERY IN EARLY JANUARY!**40' x 40' x 15' DOUBLE TRUSS Container Shelter*Upgraded from 5 to 7 trusses for stronger frame! Typical dual truss models this size have 10ft arch spacing, this model has 6.5ft arch spacing = 7 arches total!HEAVY DUTY 30 oz PVC Solid White CoverNEWLY UPGRADED PREMIUM MODELPVC Fabric Container Mounted Canopy ShelterTwist-lock Mount StyleWe are proud to offer this Covermore brand fabric storage shelter for sale.  This storage shelter comes with a SOLID WHITE 30 oz. PVC cover.  Get the best bang for your buck with this 30 oz. PVC cover that will last much longer than the industry standard, approx. 10-15 years.Why Buy From Us:We are a family owned and operated company in Oklahoma and have been selling on eBay since 1999. We are dedicated to superior customer service.  We have sold over 950 of these storage buildings in the last 5 years, shipped to all 50 states & personally use them for our own storage needs. Contact us with your questions and we'll be glad to discuss them with you.Financing Now Available! We now offer business financing through our partnership with MATRIX BUSINESS CAPITAL. Our rep is awesome and can get you approved within 24 hours. Contact us for more info. We offer a standard 1 year warranty against any major defects. We have parts on-hand and available should you need them. We have replacement covers available as well. PLEASE NOTE: This is a new model so many of the images used are for reference of the dual truss arches, and 7 arch model, as well it is SOLID WHITE.SOLID WHITE COVER....why is that important?The solid white cover is very important because the colored (usually green) ends on most of these storage buildings being offered for sale is a weak point in the cover.  The colored ends do not have the same ability to withstand UV rays as the solid white.  We have received report after report from previous owners of hail penetrating the colored ends, but not the main white part.....reports of the cover tearing at the seam where it transitions to the colored end.....& we have personally noticed excessive fading of the colored ends which can lead to premature failure of the cover.  The frame of this 40' x 40' x 15' storage shelter is a "double truss" design.  It features a webbed truss design for added strength and ability to withstand wind & heavy snow load.  This shelter is designed to secure between (2) 40' shipping containers.  The frame has a 15' overall height.  Once assembled between containers this will have an overall height of 23' at the middle on the 8'6" container and approx. 24' on the 9'6" containers.  This storage building can also be secured between 2 semi trailers, pony walls, concrete block walls or whatever you can think of.  It can also be secured directly to the ground.The double truss arches consist of (2) 2.36" 17 gauge galvanized steel pipes with diagonal cross supports.  The purlins are constructed of 2" round 17 gauge galvanized steel pipes.  The arches are spaced 6.5 ft. apart. *** PLEASE NOTE THE SHIPPING CONTAINERS ARE NOT INCLUDED. We only sell the galvanized steel framework and pvc fabric cover. ***PE vs PVC fabric and why we choose PVC:Both (PE) polyethylene and PVC are waterproof, but PVC is more so. Additionally, PVC is much more fire-resistant than polyethylene because the chlorine atoms it releases during a fire inhibit the process of combustion. Poly vinyl (PVC) is made from the polymerizing of vinyl chloride monomer. Additional stabilizers and plasticizers are added to increase its light and heat resistant properties and increase its elasticity. These properties make PVC suitable for various industrial applications. PVC fabric is durable and designed to last a long time - up to 30 years. PVC fabric is thicker than PE fabric, weighing between 20-28 ounces psf. Compared to PE, PVC fabric has a higher tear strength, making it a popular choice for buildings that are exposed to high UV rays, strong winds and other extreme conditions. PE fabric is a lighter type of architectural fabric, commonly weighing 12 to 15 ounces psf, with a shorter lifespan than PVC. PE fabric does self-clean very well when it rains and it is about 5% more light translucent than PVC. This model comes in 2 crates and weighs over 3,450 lbs.There is a flat rate $1,395 freight shipping charge for this item to an address with a forklift available. This crate will ship via flatbed for safer transit and easier to unload than enclosed trailer. Payment TermsWe accept all major credit cards or a bank wire transfer for payment. Title: Older King Martin Industries Circulator Furnace
Body: All the grates are near perfect. The blower does work, but it was wired directly into the house and needs to be rewired. Simple though. It doesn’t look to have been used very much at all. It’s got 2 ports on top to hook up to ductwork so it’s truly designed to be a wood fired central heater. But you could always just hook up the blower and blow the heat all over your shop. This is not one of the newer models built by the United States Stove Company. This is the real deal manufactured by Martin Industries of Sheffield, Alabama. Back when they were still in business. This is a good stove and way cheaper than a new one, and much better too. I’ll bet it would last 10x as long.

Title: New 1-Trip Shipping Containers, Storage Solutions, Storage Containers
Body: XCaliber Container has over 15 years of experience in the Modified Steel Shipping Container industry and is the leading supplier of steel shipping containers in Texas and the surrounding states.Our 1-Trip Steel Shipping Container features steel cargo doors, one-trip quality floors, and a clean appearance.All 1-Trip Steel Shipping Containers are considered New Steel Shipping Containers in the US, with only one load of cargo having been shipped in them previously. There are no Steel Shipping Containers available in the US that have not had at least one load of cargo shipped in them.All of XCaliber Containers 1-Trip Steel Shipping Containers include the following:- XCaliber's 1-Year Service Warranty against leaks- 10-Point Quality Control Inspection & Repair- Factory Paint (Color can vary depending on supply)- Lock Box for Added SecurityContainer Condition: The 1-Trip Steel Shipping Containers are normally considered to be in new condition with the possibility of some minor signs of one load of cargo previously shipped in them. Some minor scrapes and/or very few small dents may be visible. The container floor may show signs of a forklift previously loading/unloading pallets and/or minor scratches.Warranty Disclaimer: XCaliber Container warranties our 1-Trip Steel Shipping Containers for 1 year against leaks. If a leak occurs during the 1-Year Warranty period, our service truck is scheduled to fix the unit at the customer's request.We offer tilt-bed delivery, which is included in quotes online or over the phone at 940-445-8990. Our Sales Specialists are available to assist you when choosing a container, with delivery information, and financing options if desired.For more information or for a free quote online, visit Title: Used WWT & Refurbished Shipping Containers, Storage Containers, Connex
Body: XCaliber Container offers 20’ & 40’ Used & Refurbished Shipping Containers. Our Used Shipping Containers ship directly from the container yard. The color varies depending on the original factory paint. These units are used so they do have some rust and dents/dings but they are guaranteed to have no holes or leaks on delivery, making them perfect for storage needs.Our Refurbished Shipping Containers are high-quality used shipping containers that we have hand-picked for our refurbishing process. This process includes removal of present rust, cargo door servicing, roof or wall repairs, and fresh paint. There are two different grades of refurbished containers, Premium Refurbished and Basic Refurbished. Premium Refurbished Shipping Containers are the highest quality used units we offer and are painted tan. Basic Refurbished Shipping Containers are mid quality and are painted gray. Our Refurbished Shipping Containers feature a 1-Year Service warranty against leaks and rodents.  XCaliber Container is one of the leading suppliers of shipping containers for purchase and rent in Texas. We also offer custom shipping containers, including cabins and offices. Additionally, financing options are available for all of our shipping containers, including customs. Our typical service area includes Texas, New Mexico, and Oklahoma. For more information, visit our website at www.xcalibercontainer.com or call 940-445-8990.As always, thank you for your time and business!............Shipping container, Sea Container, Steel Title: New 1-Trip Shipping Containers, Storage Solutions, Storage Containers
Body: XCaliber Container has over 15 years of experience in the Modified Steel Shipping Container industry and is the leading supplier of steel shipping containers in Texas and the surrounding states.Our 1-Trip Steel Shipping Container features steel cargo doors, one-trip quality floors, and a clean appearance.All 1-Trip Steel Shipping Containers are considered New Steel Shipping Containers in the US, with only one load of cargo having been shipped in them previously. There are no Steel Shipping Containers available in the US that have not had at least one load of cargo shipped in them.All of XCaliber Containers 1-Trip Steel Shipping Containers include the following:- XCaliber's 1-Year Service Warranty against leaks- 10-Point Quality Control Inspection & Repair- Factory Paint (Color can vary depending on supply)- Lock Box for Added SecurityContainer Condition: The 1-Trip Steel Shipping Containers are normally considered to be in new condition with the possibility of some minor signs of one load of cargo previously shipped in them. Some minor scrapes and/or very few small dents may be visible. The container floor may show signs of a forklift previously loading/unloading pallets and/or minor scratches.Warranty Disclaimer: XCaliber Container warranties our 1-Trip Steel Shipping Containers for 1 year against leaks. If a leak occurs during the 1-Year Warranty period, our service truck is scheduled to fix the unit at the customer's request.We offer tilt-bed delivery, which is included in quotes online or over the phone at 940-445-8990. Our Sales Specialists are available to assist you when choosing a container, with delivery information, and financing options if desired.For more information or for a free quote online, visit Title: Used WWT & Refurbished Shipping Containers, Storage Containers, Connex
Body: XCaliber Container offers 20’ & 40’ Used & Refurbished Shipping Containers. Our Used Shipping Containers ship directly from the container yard. The color varies depending on the original factory paint. These units are used so they do have some rust and dents/dings but they are guaranteed to have no holes or leaks on delivery, making them perfect for storage needs.Our Refurbished Shipping Containers are high-quality used shipping containers that we have hand-picked for our refurbishing process. This process includes removal of present rust, cargo door servicing, roof or wall repairs, and fresh paint. There are two different grades of refurbished containers, Premium Refurbished and Basic Refurbished. Premium Refurbished Shipping Containers are the highest quality used units we offer and are painted tan. Basic Refurbished Shipping Containers are mid quality and are painted gray. Our Refurbished Shipping Containers feature a 1-Year Service warranty against leaks and rodents.  XCaliber Container is one of the leading suppliers of shipping containers for purchase and rent in Texas. We also offer custom shipping containers, including cabins and offices. Additionally, financing options are available for all of our shipping containers, including customs. Our typical service area includes Texas, New Mexico, and Oklahoma. For more information, visit our website at www.xcalibercontainer.com or call 940-445-8990.As always, thank you for your time and business!.................Shipping container, Sea Container, Steel Title: New 1-Trip Shipping Containers, Storage Solutions, Storage Containers
Body: XCaliber Container has over 15 years of experience in the Modified Steel Shipping Container industry and is the leading supplier of steel shipping containers in Texas and the surrounding states.Our 1-Trip Steel Shipping Container features steel cargo doors, one-trip quality floors, and a clean appearance.All 1-Trip Steel Shipping Containers are considered New Steel Shipping Containers in the US, with only one load of cargo having been shipped in them previously. There are no Steel Shipping Containers available in the US that have not had at least one load of cargo shipped in them.All of XCaliber Containers 1-Trip Steel Shipping Containers include the following:- XCaliber's 1-Year Service Warranty against leaks- 10-Point Quality Control Inspection & Repair- Factory Paint (Color can vary depending on supply)- Lock Box for Added SecurityContainer Condition: The 1-Trip Steel Shipping Containers are normally considered to be in new condition with the possibility of some minor signs of one load of cargo previously shipped in them. Some minor scrapes and/or very few small dents may be visible. The container floor may show signs of a forklift previously loading/unloading pallets and/or minor scratches.Warranty Disclaimer: XCaliber Container warranties our 1-Trip Steel Shipping Containers for 1 year against leaks. If a leak occurs during the 1-Year Warranty period, our service truck is scheduled to fix the unit at the customer's request.We offer tilt-bed delivery, which is included in quotes online or over the phone at 940-445-8990. Title: Used WWT & Refurbished Shipping Containers, Storage Containers, Connex
Body: XCaliber Container offers 20’ & 40’ Used & Refurbished Shipping Containers. Our Used Shipping Containers ship directly from the container yard. The color varies depending on the original factory paint. These units are used so they do have some rust and dents/dings but they are guaranteed to have no holes or leaks on delivery, making them perfect for storage needs.Our Refurbished Shipping Containers are high-quality used shipping containers that we have hand-picked for our refurbishing process. This process includes removal of present rust, cargo door servicing, roof or wall repairs, and fresh paint. There are two different grades of refurbished containers, Premium Refurbished and Basic Refurbished. Premium Refurbished Shipping Containers are the highest quality used units we offer and are painted tan. Basic Refurbished Shipping Containers are mid quality and are painted gray. Our Refurbished Shipping Containers feature a 1-Year Service warranty against leaks and rodents.  XCaliber Container is one of the leading suppliers of shipping containers for purchase and rent in Texas. We also offer custom shipping containers, including cabins and offices. Additionally, financing options are available for all of our shipping containers, including customs. Our typical service area includes Texas, New Mexico, and Oklahoma. PVC coverImproved Design:14.75 'x 14.75' Winch Door System  Walk-through Man Door - BOTH ENDS!We are proud to offer this Covermore brand fabric storage shelter for sale.  This storage shelter comes with a SOLID WHITE 30 oz. PVC cover.  This is a heavier longer lasting cover than the standard 10.5 oz. PE cover that comes on most of these shelters.  Why Buy From Us:We are a family owned and operated company in Oklahoma and have been selling on eBay since 1999. We are dedicated to superior customer service.  We have sold over 1,000 of these storage buildings in the last 5 years, shipped to all 50 states & personally use them for our own storage needs. Contact us with your questions and we'll be glad to discuss them with you.We offer a standard 1 year warranty against any major defects. The manufacturer estimates a standard life expectancy of 10-15 years on the 30 oz. PVC canvas cover.  Improved Winch Door SystemThis building has an improved winch style roll-up door system.  Usually the first thing that gets damaged on these building systems are the large roll-up doors.  This door system instead of a large flap of material that hangs down has rails similar to that of a garage door that helps keep the door flap centered and stabilized so the winds don't blow on the door as much ultimately causing damage.  This door system will allow you to easily roll the door up a few feet or half way and not worry about a large gust of wind causing damage.  The standard roll up door style can sustain damage if not secured properly.  This upgraded winch style door system on both ends increases the price, but is going to save you a lot of heart-ache and frustration and is going to ultimately last much longer.Description:Model Size: Fabric Storage Shelter: 40’W x 80’L x 21’HArch Spacing: 10’Dual truss frameTruss Arch Tubes: 60, 16-gauge galvanized steelPurlin Tubes: 60, 16-gauge galvanized steelFront Wall: 14.75’ x 14.75’ winch door + man doorBack Wall: 14.75’ x 14.75’ winch door + man doorAll parts pre-drilled for easy assemblyRatchet strap system secures the ground bars to the footplatesCover: 30 oz. PVCFire retardantWater resistantUV protectedSolid white colorPE vs PVC fabric and why we choose PVC for our Fabric Storage Shelters:Both (PE) polyethylene and PVC are waterproof, but PVC is more so. Additionally, PVC is muchmore fire-resistant than polyethylene because the chlorine atoms it releases during a fire inhibitthe process of combustion.Poly vinyl (PVC) is made from the polymerizing of vinyl chloride monomer. Additionalstabilizers and plasticizers are added to increase its light and heat resistant properties andincrease its elasticity. These properties make PVC suitable for various industrial applications.PVC fabric is durable and designed to last a long time. PVC fabric is thicker than PE fabric,weighing between 20-28 ounces psf. Compared to PE, PVC fabric has a higher tear strength,making it a popular choice for buildings that are exposed to high UV rays, strong winds andother extreme conditions.PE fabric is a lighter type of architectural fabric, commonly weighing 12 to 15 ounces psf, with ashorter lifespan than PVC. PE fabric does self-clean very well when it rains and it is about 5%more light translucent than PVC.Solid White Cover and Why It’s Important:The solid white cover is very important because the dyed ends (usually green) that you see onsome tension fabric buildings is a weak point in the cover. The dyed ends do not have the sameability to withstand UV rays as the undyed white fabric. We have received report after reportfrom previous owners of hail penetrating the colored ends, but not the main white part, reportsof the cover tearing at the seam where it transitions to the dyed end, and we have personallynoticed excessive fading which can lead to premature failure of the cover.Shipping:This building will be delivered via flatbed for a flat rate of $1,600.
